- Remote/hybrid: very common (great for tier-2/3 cities)  
- Top fields:
  - Software Development (Frontend / Backend / Full Stack)
  - Data Analytics / Data Science / AI / ML
  - Digital Marketing / Social Media / Content
  - Business Development / Sales / Operations
  - HR / Recruitment
