## 2. Who Can Apply

Almost anyone — no strict barriers, success depends on profile quality.

Eligible:
- 11th/12th students (mostly content/marketing via connections)
- 1st/2nd year college (startups, learning roles)
- 3rd/4th year (B.Tech, BCA, B.Com, etc.)
- Final year / PG (MCA, MBA, etc.)
